This slackbuild download and builds all available mplayer skins in http://mplayerhq.hu

You may wan to edit the value of the variable DEFSKIN to change to default skin. 
By default, we have:
DEFSKIN=${DEFSKIN:-iTunes}  ## Default skin for mplayer

After you obtain all packages of all skins (you install the default skin you choosed 
and any other Mplayer skin you want ...)

Enjoy !
